ygData.subject: RE: [EverQuest] Re: Active servers?
ygData.msgSnippet: There are not that many low level types around who can benefit from the old content any more, which explains those particular empty zones. Try Wall of
ygData.messageBody:
There are not that many low level types around who can
benefit from the old content any more, which explains
those particular empty zones.

Try Wall of Slaughter, MPG, RSS, Icefall, Vald, FC
etc. for zones that have players in them pretty much
all the time.

Quwi
